{"tid":277771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機電署：香港自動梯99%因乘客而故障　市民應「企定定」","createTime":"2017-06-10T02:03:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T05:13:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":8,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"86f1342d8e4ff2305835ad162a59b2ea6a3397b0","tid":277771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170610/s00001/9c00dae0d01e8394f9e57fd614baebd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F9c00dae0d01e8394f9e57fd614baebd2.jpg&h=3ec2356d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機電署昨公布朗豪坊自動梯事故調查，機電署副署長（規管服務）薜永恒指，去年香港有約1600宗關於自動梯的事故，當中約99%的事故，都因乘客而故障，因機件故障引起的事故只有3宗，屬極為罕見。<br />\n<br />\n機電署副署長（規管服務）薜永恒接受港台訪問時多番強調，香港法例訂明相關檢查、保養守則，只要各個持分者，即自動梯負責人、承辦商、專業工程人員按法例「做好本分」，按法例進行保養、檢察工作，自動梯不應發生意外，「每位持分者做好本分，自動梯絕對可安全運行」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，乘自動梯的市民亦是持分者之一，他呼籲市民乘自動梯時要「緊握扶手、企定定、留意周邊的環境」，尤其推嬰兒車的市民切勿乘自動梯。<br />\n<br />\n薜永恒透露，署方每7年巡查自動梯一次，上一次巡查朗豪坊電梯是2011年。他指，過往署方巡查沒發現長自動梯有特別問題，是次意外令署方反思在監管自動梯方面須要投放更多資源。<br />\n<br />\n機電署助理署長（氣體及一般法例）彭耀雄指，本港現時有64部長自動梯，署方現時就長自動梯的檢查加密至一年一次，今年已完成巡查39部長自動梯。<br />\n<br />\n對於有工會認為只有兩名工人承擔責任是不公道。薜永恒回應指，署方翻查了超過2500小時的相關閉路電視片段及工作日誌，調查工人的保養、檢察工作程序，「深信兩位工程師無履行法例應有責任」，薜指政府要給業界一個清楚的信息，若有不當行為必須承擔法例責任。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，署方相信本港絕大部分從業員均是盡忠職守。"},{"pid":"19ed62ab08f5c02e7af3d0f0cdc0f5144f17d079","tid":277771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:04:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497058124821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497058124821&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f0179618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497058124821&h=60718aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497058124821</a>"},{"pid":"ce36fa406573342f883d4cd3932bee9f3f3d4be1","tid":277771,"uid":15862,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:04:40.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都賴市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b884d974b5f1329fb5cea1b2a7f8b9665cedc525","tid":277771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c86e9fe1c20eb16225e27891a0699c25048dd913","tid":277771,"uid":39871,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"唔載人就唔會壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突破盲點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b24d769f50a50c98e5358abdd0e7cc21763452d","tid":277771,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"仆街啦你"},{"pid":"b49218702091f2070519f38e8ac26e3c0834e204","tid":277771,"uid":68528,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fcbd2101a77b3c36bb9d6a136c40e4a9761244f","tid":277771,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:06:54.000Z","msg":"署方相信本港絕大部分從業員均是盡忠職守<br />\n<br />\n笑咗"},{"pid":"73d19b55118c428e04760bab0933d920951da805","tid":277771,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:07:35.000Z","msg":"故障同嚴重事故可以混為一談<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b694850c1c86834b05ba13c3cb1bf7f94896cab2","tid":277771,"uid":490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"不如轉窄d 條電梯，得瘦人可以企"},{"pid":"73596e7f95b858143417f923b64bb6ad630675dd","tid":277771,"uid":1002,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:11:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><bl