，即自動梯負責人、承辦商、專業工程人員按法例「做好本分」，按法例進行保養、檢察工作，自動梯不應發生意外，「每位持分者做好本分，自動梯絕對可安全運行」。<br />\n<br />\n他指，乘自動梯的市民亦是持分者之一，他呼籲市民乘自動梯時要「緊握扶手、企定定、留意周邊的環境」，尤其推嬰兒車的市民切勿乘自動梯。<br />\n<br />\n薜永恒透露，署方每7年巡查自動梯一次，上一次巡查朗豪坊電梯是2011年。他指，過往署方巡查沒發現長自動梯有特別問題，是次意外令署方反思在監管自動梯方面須要投放更多資源。<br />\n<br />\n機電署助理署長（氣體及一般法例）彭耀雄指，本港現時有64部長自動梯，署方現時就長自動梯的檢查加密至一年一次，今年已完成巡查39部長自動梯。<br />\n<br />\n對於有工會認為只有兩名工人承擔責任是不公道。薜永恒回應指，署方翻查了超過2500小時的相關閉路電視片段及工作日誌，調查工人的保養、檢察工作程序，「深信兩位工程師無履行法例應有責任」，薜指政府要給業界一個清楚的信息，若有不當行為必須承擔法例責任。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，署方相信本港絕大部分從業員均是盡忠職守。</blockquote><br />\n呢種咁的回應將會變成未來所有大小機構同政府部門的abc餐<br />\n<br />\n第一<br />\n「當中約99%的事故，都因乘客而故障，因機件故障引起的事故只有3宗，屬極為罕見。」<br />\n99%乘客引起的係咩原因? 有雜物zip入級邊? 家有人多手撳暫停掣?<br />\n呢單野可以點樣人為?<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n「每位持分者做好本分，自動梯絕對可安全運行」<br />\n「緊握扶手、企定定、留意周邊的環境」<br />\n咩本分? 「只要每個人做好本人, 社會就會繁榮安定」有咩分別?<br />\n想講乘客唔應該行電梯下嗎? 留意周邊環境係咪叫人自己留意佢幾時會墮後要自己保命?<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n推bb車係怕佢Hold唔實仆街, 會zip係級邊<br />\n同你斷鏈有咩關係? 怪架bb車重得濟? 咁不如安全指引寫明唔畀肥佬搭啦"},{"pid":"ca38f4f0d36fe2cfcad8a154e5c60c1bcfe280f1","tid":277771,"uid":34490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"機電署真係好撚廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0366a6159f17e9394967b642884bebf0805c28","tid":277771,"uid":17496,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"哈,口吻咁似ifan boy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4776e4b26bf900e17ab05dece8b871cf2c4d255","tid":277771,"uid":64648,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜鳩都賴市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係囉<br />\n有啲on9自己仆親都格硬要屈部電梯有事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一件事一件事咁睇，有幾多人會行朗豪坊條長電梯呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed248534f6d8eb8fde2e6dadd8c427b95c0a4cd","tid":277771,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"同意 行乜鳩你班友"},{"pid":"1073235d046e0ec70aa2bd1e2cc33a76a502cc4a","tid":277771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06bc288e6b09b2fca4c673609697736d68f7842","tid":277771,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"咪撚出街就啱"},{"pid":"0b278f3f621809380d1852cc2ea39e94a7d259f4","tid":277771,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:40:46.000Z","msg":"左行右企撚系鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀藉口香港特區政府將問題賴落市民身上"},{"pid":"5b673c1140a71a75f42e02a407176d33189469ad","tid":277771,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜鳩都賴市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢無錯wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定？全香港冇邊幾條電梯係啲人企定定，朗豪坊係其中一條。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">企定定又話則埋一邊企</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乜撚都係入市民數<br />\n咁不如一早整單行自動梯啦<br />\n咁咪唔會話則埋一邊唔平衡，又唔會話人唔企定囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n企定定 = 企定定<br />\n慣性靠右企先系側埋一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd41686eac4ae1265e86d42f0dcb893ce2ab0694","tid":277771,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:43:12.000Z","msg":"屌啦媽，機電署食濕米<br />\n講埋啲廢話<br />\n呢單野唔出事你就廢話都唔撚講<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一掌轟撚爆你班柒頭<br />\n用家本身就應該係設計考慮範疇內，你話班友係上面開p，完全唔撚柒乎合個用途就話姐<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母！懶靚咁起到條柒梯九廿幾丈高，搭幾個通頂都未撚到頂，好啦而家訓撚低哂就屌鳩我係上面行？你老母訓撚柒醒未？"},{"pid":"830a29a0415751d68d6ddbc00ab64cc51cefe3f3","tid":277771,"uid":85131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:44:47.000Z","msg":"今日金鐘咪有單電梯食人事件囉"},{"pid":"5eb0ac98b2c69fe64cfe190080c656861eca49b3","tid":277771,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:45:02.000Z","msg":"設計咁長<br />\n負荷唔到就咪整咁長"},{"pid":"beaf5b2651909fdf6318d96121becde870e93798","tid":277771,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"一定係用家問題<br />\n無人用就唔會壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28488ba3aa4b22775fd63feca277077fe4adc7a","tid":277771,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:54:07.000Z","msg":"置換思維：香港個人電腦99%因使用者而當機　用家應「勿超頻」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153136ef0000f6c54057cd97dd8a012a7632950f","tid":277771,"uid":51291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:02:11.000Z","msg":"有時塞哂等一邊既時間好似仲耐過兩邊企哂人"},{"pid":"d83a94b51be80c140b1b5625595c0df59b791f69","tid":277771,"uid":36287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:05:55.000Z","msg":"根本得出事個條長期無人行"},{"pid":"68e29d837c49ca677cc33291e9391076e66fa7b1","tid":277771,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:06:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時塞哂等一邊既時間好似仲耐過兩邊企哂人</blockquote><br />\n但當大部分人 沒有邏輯 只有慣性<br />\n會屌番你轉頭「做乜唔企右手邊」<br />\n🙄"},{"pid":"098438d24b9b66c00d4ae7a3c37be8ca357628c1","tid":277771,"uid":5026,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"到時企定定又會話斷果格過重架喇，不如set話過50kg就唔準搭啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老味電梯設計出黎就係預左比人行架啦<br />\n唔比人行就搭𨋢啦<br />\n<br />\n整電梯間公司都無話唔比人行<br />\n但負責檢查維修果個部門就話係人嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n如果係間電梯公司講係用家問題你話仲會唔會有人買佢產品<br />\n產品改進同符合用家需求呢樣野就係公司要做架啦<br />\n符合唔到用家需求就無人買架啦<br />\n<br />\n而家單野明明就檢查同維修不力<br />\n朗豪城單野之後仲有人返去偷證物（單野又不了了之）<br />\n<br />\n有腦嘅都唔會賴落市民果度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a596e52fe3406cb56800bda488faa0739335ce65","tid":277771,"uid":61724,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:15:20.000Z","msg":"正常角度真係唔應該行"},{"pid":"4dd7bccdccbd6a17ca7b23ccca6d9fc2ac2379c7","tid":277771,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defc8f1e9390bb5d78d893cef57f1ab7460c8fee","tid":277771,"uid":22736,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"部電梯自已識行你做乜鳩仲睇上面行咁急自已去行樓梯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f749702a39b43dee5cff0a7159d83bdd5195747","tid":277771,"uid":71596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:17:53.000Z","msg":"其實機電署錯唔哂<br />\n眼見係好多老野自己企唔穩又唔扶同蝗蝻小童 係上面玩 整停"},{"pid":"dc4b300800e2be42c75d3d6354a5e894e39ee93c","tid":277771,"uid":30847,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"人地一早同你講唔好行，到依家出事就怨返機電署將責任推比市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d417fec4bd8f6fae275395e3f8fce347dcdbd5","tid":277771,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:18:34.000Z","msg":"明明朗豪坊條扶手電梯先係特別少人行"},{"pid":"d6729fbbf8411bbb49c4f804721457f3d58adcc2","tid":277771,"uid":60183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔講以為機動遊戲黎"},{"pid":"46a1f1337fd68bec51b2524dcfb9eaa7e0edbd79","tid":277771,"uid":56912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T03:36:48.000Z","msg":"不如唔好用扶手梯，全部人行樓梯算啦"},{"pid":"1eafd97ec22a486a3f7040eb331f7f403fa7e3a4","tid":277771,"uid":85131,